{% endif %}

{% if get_quest_stage("MS13", false) >= 100 %}
* Hilde knows the Golden Claw was returned to the Riverwood Trader. She's pleased that Lucan and Camilla have their prized possession back, especially if Sven's romantic rival Faendal wasn't involved in its recovery.
