{% endif %}

{% if get_quest_stage("CW03", true) >= 10 and get_quest_stage("CW03", true) < 100 %}
* Hilde overhears travelers discussing increased military movements and tensions between Whiterun and the Stormcloaks. She fears the war is coming closer to Riverwood.
{% endif %}
